  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Sales Consultant",
  "description": "<p>Convert8 is growing fast, and we’re looking for a driven <strong>Sales Consultant</strong> to help businesses improve customer engagement using our AI-powered automation platform.</p><p>This is an <strong>remote inbound sales role</strong> — you won’t need to cold call or hunt for leads.<br />All leads come from marketing campaigns, inbound enquiries, and partner referrals.</p><h3>What You’ll Do</h3><ul><li><p>Speak with inbound leads to understand their business needs</p></li><li><p>Run product demos and clearly explain how Convert8 creates value</p></li><li><p>Recommend the right solution and close deals</p></li><li><p>Build long-term relationships with clients</p></li><li><p>Continuously learn about AI, automation, and customer engagement trends</p></li></ul><h3>What Makes This Role Attractive</h3><ul><li><p>No cold calling – leads are provided</p></li><li><p>Commission-only with generous revenue share</p></li><li><p>High earning potential for self-driven consultants</p></li><li><p>Fully performance-based, flexible, and independent</p></li></ul><h3>Who This Role Is For</h3><p>You’ll do well here if you:</p><ul><li><p>Enjoy building relationships and having consultative sales conversations</p></li><li><p>Are comfortable working independently and owning your results</p></li><li><p>Are curious about technology, AI, and automation</p></li><li><p>Want uncapped earnings based on performance</p></li></ul><h3>Required Skills & Traits</h3><ul><li><p>Strong communication and presentation skills</p></li><li><p>Self-motivated with an entrepreneurial mindset</p></li><li><p>Comfortable learning and using new software tools</p></li><li><p>Able to thrive in a commission-based environment</p></li></ul><h3>Bonus (Nice to Have)</h3><ul><li><p>Experience in B2B sales, SaaS, or tech solutions</p></li><li><p>Background in sales consulting, account management, or partnerships</p></li></ul><h3>Interested in Joining Us?</h3><p>Email your CV to <a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">yongjie@convert8.io</a></p>",
