    "description": "<p>Brands succeed when they build genuine relationships with their customers. At Convert8, we believe exceptional customer support drives both sales and loyalty.</p><p>When we launched in 2019, we saw a gap: businesses were losing sales in every conversation that went unanswered or unguided. That’s why we built ALEXIO AI — an intelligent chatbot that never sleeps, never misses an opportunity, and turns every customer interaction into a potential sale.</p><p>Leading brands like KFC and McDonald’s across the region trust ALEXIO AI to deliver in high-pressure, high-volume environments. And we’ve delivered. Today, we’ve grown to a team of problem solvers and innovators across Asia, all working toward the same goal: helping our clients build revenue through meaningful customer conversations.</p>",
